features: Silver Star Wrapping Paper Roll: Measuring 43cm x 10m /17x394 inches, suitable for small to medium sized gifts and meets all your wrapping needs, you can also cut it as needed. The iridescent sliver is so stunning and makes gifts look extra special.

Sparkling Metallic Holographic Foil Stars: Features a elegant sliver color with holographic star patterns, sparkling like stars shining in the starry sky, the iridescent design changes colors under various lighting and angles, perfect for any occasion, celebration or festival.

Premium Quality: Iridescent wrapping paper is made of well-made thick paper with vibrant colors and a shimmering metallic luster, it is sturdy and reusable, and there is grid lines included internally for clean and easy cuts, not easy to tear or break.

Gift Wrap for All Occasions: Shiny holographic foil wrapping paper for all occasions, such as birthday, anniversary, baby shower, bridal shower, wedding, Valentine's Day, Mother's Day, New Year, Thanksgiving, Christmas, graduation and so on.

Multiple Uses: The colorful metallic star wrapping paper roll can also be used for flower bouquet wrapping, party decorations, home decorations, Christmas tree decorations, book wrappers, tablecloths, DIY decorations, card making or various craft projects.
